{"search_data": "Central Revamp PM Kaushal Vikas Yojana (PMKVY) \u2013 New Age Skill Development Central govt. to revamp PM Kaushal Vikas Yojana (PMKVY) for reskilling & upskilling of youths, incentives to focus on new age technologies and new job roles for skill developmentRevamped PM Kaushal Vikas Yojana (PMKVY) for Skill DevelopmentFollowing the Budget Announcement, there is a renewed urgency to review and revamp PM Kaushal Vikas Yojana and include new job roles. The central govt. is expected to place new programme / scheme by 3rd quarter as reskilling is its priority. The govt. aims to create workforce which is capable of accessing new opportunities and insulate it from technical shocks.The govt. is considering massive reforms in PM Kaushal Vikas Yojana and changes are likely to be applicable from next fiscal. A new dedicated curriculum is going to be developed across various sectors. The central govt. has allocated Rs. 12,000 crore to train 10 million youths under PMKVY between 2016 and 2020.It is expected that the central govt. will dole out such incentives to sector skills council which are undertaking such training. The scope of PMKVY Scheme could be widened which would make it more effective. The lifecycle of centrally sponsored schemes is similar to that of the 14th Finance Commission which is ending on 31 March 2020.PM Kaushal Vikas Yojana RevampedThe commission is carrying out review of all schemes which includes duplication, congruence between outlay and desired outcomes. Moreover, review is also being carried out for financial threshold for all these skill development schemes.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://economictimes.indiatimes.com/industry/services/education/skill-development-ministrys-flagship-scheme-to-focus-on-new-age-skills/articleshow/70221128.cms  at  "}